Package org.opengis.cite.cdb10.util.metadataXml

package org.opengis.cite.cdb10.util.metadataXml
Classes used for reading data and values from CDB Metadata directory files. Can be used on a CDB under test, or pointed to the embedded sample CDB in this ETS.
